English: The harmony of eggs, rice and ingredients is wonderful. It works better than a roughly cooked dish.
Korean: 달걀과 밥 그리고 재료의 조화가 훌륭하다. 대충 만든 요리보다 효과가 좋다.

English: Roughly roasted rice and meat. There seems to be a way to make it more delicious.

English: Fried rice and meat well. It is made delicious and the effect is good.

English: Steak made with the least amount of meat. The recovery effect is great.

Korean: 좋은 고기와 향신료가 곁들여진 최고의 스테이크. 이보다 더 좋은 음식은 없을듯!

English: Baked the eggs in olive oil. When you eat, mood improves and damage increases during 1 stage.

English: She likes the fragrant herb tea. The critical probability increases during 1 stage.
